        Print an arc with 1.0 values on the filter.
        Parameters:
        filter - The filter, may not be squared.
        x - The X coordinate of the upper-left corner of the arc's framing rectangle.
        y - The Y coordinate of the upper-left corner of the arc's framing rectangle.
        width - The overall width of the full ellipse of which this arc is a partial section.
        height - The overall height of the full ellipse of which this arc is a partial section.
        start - The starting angle of the arc in degrees.
        extent - The angular extent of the arc in degrees.
